JOHANNESBURG Capitec has clinched the top banking spot, beating FNB in this year's Internet Banking SITE-isfaction survey.The survey measures customer reaction to digital banking services in South Africa. The industry considers the report an essential feedback tool. READ: Capitec still South Africa's most popular bank: NielsenCapitec secured the top spot in the digital banking category.The bank scored 81 out of a possible 100.Capitec received another accolade for the best bank in the mobile banking category.However, FNB managed to beat Capitec in the internet banking section.eNCA